statements: SELECT * FROM ai_performance;
SELECT algorithm_name, accuracy, training_time FROM ai_performance;
SELECT performance_metric, evaluation_time FROM ai_performance;
SELECT * FROM ai_performance WHERE accuracy > 0.8;
SELECT algorithm_id, algorithm_name, performance_metric FROM ai_performance ORDER BY algorithm_id DESC;
SELECT algorithm_name, accuracy FROM ai_performance WHERE accuracy > 0.90
SELECT * FROM ai_performance ORDER BY evaluation_time DESC
SELECT algorithm_name, performance_metric, accuracy FROM ai_performance WHERE algorithm_name LIKE 'Logistic%'
SELECT training_time, evaluation_time FROM ai_performance WHERE performance_metric = 'F1-Score' AND accuracy >= 0.85
SELECT algorithm_name, accuracy, training_time, evaluation_time FROM ai_performance WHERE training_time < 100
SELECT * FROM AI_Algorithms;
SELECT algorithm_name, performance_score FROM AI_Algorithms ORDER BY performance_score DESC;
SELECT algorithm_name, accuracy FROM AI_Algorithms WHERE performance_score > 0.8;
SELECT algorithm_name, execution_time, accuracy FROM AI_Algorithms JOIN Algorithm_Performance ON AI_Algorithms.algorithm_id = Algorithm_Performance.algorithm_id;
SELECT algorithm_name, description FROM AI_Algorithms WHERE description IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM AI_Algorithms WHERE performance_score > 0.8 ORDER BY algorithm_id DESC;
SELECT algorithm_name, description FROM AI_Algorithms WHERE algorithm_name LIKE 'S%' AND description IS NOT NULL;
SELECT AVG(accuracy), MAX(memory_usage) FROM Algorithm_Performance WHERE execution_time < 1000;
SELECT algorithm_id, AVG(accuracy) AS avg_accuracy FROM Algorithm_Performance GROUP BY algorithm_id HAVING AVG(accuracy) > 0.7;
SELECT * FROM AI_Algorithms AS Algorithms JOIN Algorithm_Performance AS Performance ON Algorithms.algorithm_id = Performance.algorithm_id WHERE Algorithms.algorithm_name = 'Deep Learning';
SELECT * FROM AI_Algorithms;
SELECT algorithm_name, accuracy FROM AI_Algorithms WHERE accuracy > 0.8;
SELECT dataset_name, dataset_size FROM Datasets ORDER BY dataset_size DESC;
SELECT algorithm_name, performance_metric, last_updated FROM AI_Algorithms WHERE algorithm_id = 1;
SELECT result_id, algorithm_id, dataset_id, result_value, result_date FROM Model_Results WHERE result_value < 0.5;
SELECT * FROM AI_Algorithms;
SELECT algorithm_id, algorithm_name FROM AI_Algorithms WHERE accuracy > 0.8;
SELECT algorithm_name, performance_metric, last_updated FROM AI_Algorithms ORDER BY last_updated DESC;
SELECT result_id, result_value, result_date FROM Model_Results WHERE result_value BETWEEN 0.5 AND 1.0 ORDER BY result_date ASC;

SELECT AI.algorithm_name, D.dataset_name, D.dataset_size FROM AI_Algorithms AS AI JOIN Model_Results AS MR ON AI.algorithm_id = MR.algorithm_id JOIN Datasets AS D ON MR.dataset_id = D.dataset_id WHERE D.dataset_size > 1000;
SELECT * FROM ai_algorithms;
SELECT algorithm_id, algorithm_name FROM ai_algorithms ORDER BY algorithm_id DESC;
SELECT algorithm_name, accuracy FROM ai_algorithms WHERE accuracy > 0.9;
SELECT execution_time_sec, algorithm_name FROM ai_algorithms WHERE algorithm_name LIKE 'K%';
SELECT * FROM algorithm_tests INNER JOIN ai_algorithms ON algorithm_tests.algorithm_id = ai_algorithms.algorithm_id;
SELECT * FROM ai_algorithms ORDER BY accuracy DESC;
SELECT algorithm_name, accuracy, execution_time_sec FROM ai_algorithms WHERE execution_time_sec > 10;
SELECT algorithm_name, test_date, test_result FROM ai_algorithms JOIN algorithm_tests ON ai_algorithms.algorithm_id = algorithm_tests.algorithm_id;
SELECT algorithm_name, hyperparameter, value FROM ai_algorithms JOIN model_parameters ON ai_algorithms.algorithm_id = model_parameters.algorithm_id WHERE value > 0.9;
SELECT algorithm_name, execution_date, status FROM ai_algorithms JOIN execution_logs ON ai_algorithms.algorithm_id = execution_logs.algorithm_id WHERE status = 'success';
SELECT * FROM ai_algorithms;
SELECT algorithm_name, created_date FROM ai_algorithms ORDER BY created_date DESC;
SELECT algorithm_name, algorithm_description FROM ai_algorithms WHERE algorithm_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM model_training WHERE training_duration > 60;
SELECT algorithm_name, accuracy_value FROM ai_algorithms JOIN model_accuracy ON ai_algorithms.algorithm_id = model_accuracy.algorithm_id ORDER BY accuracy_value DESC;
SELECT * FROM ai_algorithms;
SELECT algorithm_name, created_date FROM ai_algorithms ORDER BY created_date DESC;
SELECT algorithm_name, algorithm_description FROM ai_algorithms WHERE algorithm_id = 1;
SELECT algorithm_name, result_value FROM ai_algorithms JOIN algorithm_results ON ai_algorithms.algorithm_id = algorithm_results.algorithm_id;

SELECT model_training.training_id, ai_algorithms.algorithm_name, model_training.training_duration FROM model_training JOIN ai_algorithms ON model_training.algorithm_id = ai_algorithms.algorithm_id ORDER BY model_training.training_date DESC;
